reviewText: This is a good concgert. It is one disc of their live. Enclosed is a booklet of songs and lyrics. Please note it is a region 2 dvd. Unless you have a device that can change regions (ps4) it would be hard to watch. Please note a ps4 only has a limited times one can change regions. Overall it is about a 93 minute dvd. It has their older songs. A total of 13 songs two of them are encore. There is also a part set for omake.
